			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I went swimming in the Feerott river w/ invis song on, turning it off to kill a couple mobs.  I was headed toward the riverbank w/ invis off when I saw KOS Bouncer Flerb.  I turned my invis back on; it stayed on for a few tics, but then started to mess up.  Every tic, I alternately became visible or went invis.  This happened for at least 40 seconds.  I finally just gave up, turned on selo's, and went to pok.  I tried my invis song in pok, and it worked fine, but now I'm a little scared to go much of anywhere dangerous.  Has this happened to anyone else?  And could it have anything to do w/ the fact that I was swimming when this happened?</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
