				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Invis song problem<a name="51437"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 12 04 2:11 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The swimming should not have been a direct issue, but if you had agro on any mob - even if its a green con and not a real danger to you - if they see you, your invis will break. My guess by the way it was acting was you had mostly killed a mob and it started running on you and was stuck between wanting to kill you (breaking your invis) and wanting to run away from you.
<br />

<br />
Alternately if there was a mob you had agroed underwater that cannot go onto land (I've never spent enough time in Feerot to know if such things exist but think fish or sharks) then they possibly were breaking your invis even if they could not attack you because you were on land.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"></span></td>
