				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Invis song problem<a name="56879"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 16 04 10:13 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Gotta say I think YOU'RE almost right, Caliopeia.  
<br />

<br />
If you are in aggro range of a hostile mob, but not in melee range... 
<br />
and you are in assist range of OTHER mobs on his faction... 
<br />
THEY will see THRU your invis...  But your invis will NOT drop.
<br />
unless...
<br />
You have auto-attack on... or one of them attacks you (I believe they have to actually hit you to break it, but I am a little foggy here).
<br />

<br />
If there are other mobs around that are KOS to you but will not assist what you have aggro with, you would still be invis to them until you attack or are attacked.
<br />

<br />
So.. the original poster most likely had auto attack on, which would completely explain the behavior.</span></td>
